Those who served with the 3d Battalion, 3d Marines in Vietnam have an active association and bi-annual reunions.  The next get together will be in Houston in 1998.  There are still several thousand of our fellow veterans from this period that we would like to find.  Contact me at Otto@mce.com or Jeff Kelly at JKelly7@aol.com.  A history of the battalion is contained in my book &quot;No Shining Armor&quot; University Press of Kansas 1992.  Jeff Kelly also wrote a book about his experiences in Vietnam in 1968 called &quot;DMZ Diary.&quot;
